TextEng: "I... think I was warned, actually. Something woke me up."
Text: "사실... 경고받은 것 같아. 뭔가 날 깨웠거든."

TextEng: "I'm not that easy to kill. Trust me."
Text: "난 그렇게 쉽게 죽지 않아. 믿어도 돼."

TextEng: "So that's it? I'm left with nothing?"
Text: "그게 다야? 나한텐 아무것도 남은 게 없는 거야?"

TextEng: "Any idea where I could get some replacement gear?"
"I don't want your second-rate crap! I want my stuff!"
Text: "네 싸구려 쓰레기는 필요 없어! 내 물건을 원한다고!"

TextEng: "Seeing as you're already in my room and I'm undressed..."
Text: "이미 내 방에 들어왔고 난 옷도 안 입었는데..."

TextEng: "I could use some help getting dressed..."
"I have a few questions, if you don't mind."
"I want to know what your father is planning."
Text: "네 아버지가 뭘 계획하고 있는지 알고 싶어."

TextEng: "Tell me what's going on in this city."
Text: "이 도시에서 무슨 일이 일어나고 있는지 말해줘."

TextEng: "What do you mean 'the city was closed'?"
"Heroes are rarely what you expect. Remember that."
Text: "영웅은 기대했던 거랑 다른 경우가 많아. 기억해둬."

TextEng: "Thank you. I'll go there right away."
"That is a drow thief! She stole my equipment!"
"Do you always barge into your guests' rooms?"
